         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">29/10/91. ¶  ¶ You will concede, dear Prof. Tate, that after the  ¶ heavy ¶   ¶ extra- ¶ work through  ¶ several months ¶ , caused by bringing out the  ¶ much enlarged ¶  8th edition of the "Select pl...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">91.10.29</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Ralph Tate</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Barr Smith Library, University of Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>29/10/91.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will concede, dear Prof. Tate, that after the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">heavy</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">extra-</hi>
               </seg>work through <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">several months</hi>
               </seg>, caused by bringing out the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">much enlarged</hi>
               </seg> 8th edition of the "Select plants",<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">B91.13.10.</p>
               </note> much of my departmental work came into arrear;<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">sic.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> Add to this, that in an establishment with so <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">multifarious</hi>
               </seg> work and obligations, I must arrange everything when away, in such a manner, that the service and my position do not suffer; hence I cannot take out the time, as I would like, — there being never a vacation for a professional head in the Gov. Service or other interruption or cessation of his work. You will hardly credit, when I say, that I have not yet overtaken all the arrear-work, which accumulated during the one month of my absense, while proceeding for the A.A.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M attended the third Congress of the Australasian Association for the Advancement of Science, held in Christchurch, NZ, January 1891.</p>
               </note> to N.Z. So my kind friends in Adelaide must be charitable to me, otherwise I may break down all together. At best my stay in Adelaide can this time be but very brief, and so my stay in Hobart.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M paid a brief visit to Hobart, Tas., in January 1892, to attend the fourth Congress of the Australasian Association for the Advancement of Science. However, he was able to stay only for the first few days of the meeting.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Always with true friendship</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I shall be <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">delighted</hi>
               </seg> to see also <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">you</hi>
               </seg> on both places, be it even only for short moments</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Has everything become known about the gestation of the marsupial Mole.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Do you care to join the great Royal Hort soc. of London? I will gladly propose you.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Did he?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
